"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1015537","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government","false","2018-12-03","<p>The Ministry of Housing Communities and Local Government has provided no funding, contracts or procured services from the Integrity Initiative.</p>","Rossendale and Darwen","Jake Berry",,"2018-12-03T16:29:41.947Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1015537/answer","Biography information for Jake Berry","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1015537/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1015537/answer",,,,,"7","Housing, Communities and Local Government","Housing, Communities and Local Government","2018-11-27","Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government: Integrity Initiative","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Housing, Communities and Local Government, whether his Department has (a) funded, (b) awarded contracts to and (c) procured the services of the Integrity Initiative in each financial year since 2015-16.","false","Biography information for Chris Williamson","Derby North","Chris Williamson","196179"
